high_descs: Walk to the table to your left.
Grab the knife on the table.
Walk to the side of the table where the bread is.
Place the knife in the cup between the lettuce and bread.
Grab the cup with the knife in it.
With the cup with the knife in it, walk to the sink to your right.
Place the cup with the knife in it on the ledge of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup with a knife in it on the ledge of the sink.

high_descs: Turn left, walk forward to wall, turn right, walk forward to table
Pick up knife off of table
Turn right, walk forward one step, turn left to facing the table,
Put knife in cup
Pick up cup with knife inside
Turn right, walk to sink
Put cup with knife inside into the sink
anns.task_desc: Pick up knife and cup from table, move to sink

high_descs: Move slightly left and then cross the room to stand in front of the wood table in the corner.
Pick up the butter knife next to the tomato on the table.
Carry the knife to the right end of the table to stand in front of the loaf of bread.
Place the knife in the clear cup on the table that's next to the loaf of bread.
Pick up the cup with the knife in it.
Turn right and move to stand at the counter just right of the dishwasher.
Place the cup with the knife in it on the taller gray counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a knife in a cup to the gray counter.
